No. 09-986 (R46-013). Guerry Green, et al., Petitioners v. W. Russell Campbell, et al. 559 U.S. 1059, 130 S. Ct. 2088, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 3113.

176 L. Ed. 2d 580,

April 12, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of South Carolina in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 385 S.C. 428, 685 S.E.2d 163.
